title: Contributor Covenant Code of Conduct

what: Biomarker Data Set by Vermeulen et al. (2009)
title: Biomarker Data Set by Vermeulen et al. (2009)
text: vermeulen provides Biomarker data set Vermeulen et al. (2009) tidy format. data set real-time quantitative PCR experiment comprises: raw fluorescence data 24,576 amplification curves. 64 targets: 59 genes interest 5 reference genes. 366 neuroblastoma cDNA samples 18 dilution series samples.

title: Amplification curves — amplification_curves
text: data set containing raw fluorescence amplification data. Data obtained Ruijter (2013), doi:10.1016/j.ymeth.2012.08.011  original source Vermeulen (2009), doi:10.1016/S1470-2045(09)70154-8 .

title: Amplification curves — amplification_curves
text: https://medischebiologie.nl/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/qpcrdatamethods.zip https://github.com/ramiromagno/vermeulen/blob/main/data-raw/amplification_curves.csv.gz

title: Amplification curves — amplification_curves
text: data frame 24,576 amplification curves, 50 cycles : plate Plate identifier. one plate used per gene, name plate values target. well Well identifier. dye reactions SYBR Green master mix (Roche) used, value always "SYBR". cycle PCR cycle. fluor Raw fluorescence values.

title: Amplification curves — amplification_curves
text: tidy version data kept repository source {vermeulen} package. function fetches data thus requires internet connection. takes seconds run.

title: Biomarker data set — ds_biomarker
text: function retrieves biomarker data set, data set containing raw fluorescence amplification data. Data gathered Ruijter et al. (2013), doi:10.1016/j.ymeth.2012.08.011  original source Vermeulen et al. (2009), doi:10.1016/S1470-2045(09)70154-8 .

title: Biomarker data set — ds_biomarker
text: https://medischebiologie.nl/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/qpcrdatamethods.zip https://github.com/ramiromagno/vermeulen/blob/main/data-raw

title: Biomarker data set — ds_biomarker
text: data frame 24,576 amplification curves, 50 cycles : plate Plate identifier. one plate used per gene, name plate values target. well Well identifier. dye reactions SYBR Green master mix (Roche) used, value always "SYBR". target Target identifier, almost cases name gene. target_type Target type: either target interest ("toi") reference target ("ref"). sample Sample identifier. sample_type Sample type. copies Standard copy number. dilution Dilution factor. Higher number means greater dilution. cycle PCR cycle. fluor Raw fluorescence values.

title: Biomarker data set — ds_biomarker
text: tidy version data kept repository source {vermeulen} package. function fetches data thus requires internet connection. takes seconds run.

title: Reactions — reactions
text: data set containing metadata associated qPCR well respective reaction mix. Data obtained Ruijter (2013), doi:10.1016/j.ymeth.2012.08.011  original source Vermeulen (2009), doi:10.1016/S1470-2045(09)70154-8 .

title: Reactions — reactions
text: data frame 24,576 reactions 5 variables: plate Plate identifier. one plate used per gene, name plate values target. well Well identifier. dye reactions SYBR Green master mix (Roche) used, value always "SYBR". sample Sample identifier. target Target.

title: vermeulen: 'Biomarker' Data Set by 'Vermeulen et al.' (2009) — vermeulen-package
text: 'biomarker' data set 'Vermeulen et al.' (2009) doi:10.1016/S1470-2045(09)70154-8  provided 'Ruijter et al.' (2013) doi:10.1016/j.ymeth.2012.08.011 . original data set may downloaded https://medischebiologie.nl/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/qpcrdatamethods.zip. data set real-time quantitative 'polymerase' chain reaction (PCR) experiment comprises raw fluorescence data 24,576 amplification curves. data set comprises 59 genes interest 5 reference genes. gene assessed 366 'neuroblastoma' complementary DNA (cDNA) samples 18 standard dilution series samples (10-fold 5-point dilution series x 3 replicates + template controls (NTC) x 3 replicates).
